'''''Adela''''' was a [[Starship/Legends|starship]] owned by [[Refka Trell]]. It was registered on [[Elom (planet)/Legends|Elom]] with registration number RN32-000439. In [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]], this was one of many ships [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] tracked as it passed the inner flight control buoys of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Teyr/Legends|Teyr]].

